Minas Gerais 1927

Campeonato da Cidade de Belo Horizonte 1927 - Série A

Participants - all from Belo Horizonte unless city is between brackets:

ALVES NOGUEIRA Foot Ball Club (Sabará)
AMÉRICA Futebol Clube
Clube ATLÉTICO Mineiro
GUARANY Foot Ball Club
PALMEIRAS Foot Ball Club
SETE DE SETEMBRO Futebol Clube
Societá Sportiva PALESTRA ITÁLIA
Sport Club CALAFATE
Sport Club RETIRO (Nova Lima)
Sport Club SYRIO Horizontino
VILLA NOVA Atlético Clube (Nova Lima)

Notes:
- all América and Palestra matches in Belo Horizonte were played
  at their own stadia, even if those clubs were the away side, as
  only they had proper first division stadiums.
- Retiro played all home matches at Villa Nova, as they still did
  not have a stadium.
- Alves Nogueira played all home matches in Belo Horizonte, as
  Sabará had no proper stadia.

