[May 29]
América           7-1  Alves Nogueira
Guarany           1-6  Atlético          [at América]
Palmeiras         0-5  Villa Nova        [at Palestra]
Sete de Setembro  0-4  Calafate          [at Palestra]

On the week before the round of Jun 5, Syrio and Palestra, who were
members of the dissolved AMEG, were admitted back into LMDT and the
fixture was redrawn to include those clubs.

